@CdcBridge_HostAddress = http://localhost:8080
@jwt_token = your_jwt_token_here

### Get Metrics
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/api/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Events
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/api/events?page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Events with Filters
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/api/events?trackingInstanceName=MyTable&status=Pending&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Event by ID
@eventId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/api/events/{{eventId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Logs
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/api/logs?level=Error&page=1&pageSize=100
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Logs with Search
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/api/logs?messageSearch=exception&fromDate=2024-01-01&page=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Configuration
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/api/configuration
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Tracking Instances
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/api/configuration/tracking-instances
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Receivers
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/api/configuration/receivers
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Health Check (no auth required)
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Swagger UI (Development only)
GET {{CdcBridge_HostAddress}}/swagger
